Event(s):	GRIP * LATITUDE: 72.570000 * LONGITUDE: -37.620000 * DATE/TIME START: 1989-06-01T00:00:00 * DATE/TIME END: 1992-07-12T00:00:00 * ELEVATION: 3232.0 m * Penetration: 3028.8 m * Recovery: 3028.8 m * LOCATION: Greenland * CAMPAIGN: GRIP * BASIS: Sampling/drilling ice * METHOD/DEVICE: ISTUK electromechanical drill (ISTUK) (URI: https://icedrill.org/library/new-improved-version-istuk-ice-core-drill)
Parameter(s):	DEPTH, ice/snow [m] (Depth ice/snow) * GEOCODE * PI: Rasmussen, Sune Olander (https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4177-3611, sune.rasmussen@nbi.ku.dk)
